    "Html": "I'm using the DataGrid's default blue color to highlight the current row, but my hyperlinks are a bit difficult to read since they are blue as well (although light blue).  I'd like to reverse the hyperlink's foreground color from light blue to white for the currently selected row, but can't quite get the XAML right.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nI'm trying something like this:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridHyperlinkColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;linkDocNum&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Auto&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Header</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Document #&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=DocumentNum}&quot;&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ElementStyle</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> TargetType</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;TextBlock&quot;&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">EventSetter</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Event</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Hyperlink.Click&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Handler</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;DocumentNum_Click&quot; /&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Style.Triggers</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">                &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Trigger</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Property</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;dg:DataGridRow.IsSelected&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Value</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;True&quot;&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">                    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Property</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Foreground&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Value</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;White&quot;/&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">                &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Trigger</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">            &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Style.Triggers</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">        &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridHyperlinkColumn.ElementStyle</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt; <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">dg</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridHyperlinkColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe markup compiles, and I don't get a runtime error, but the foreground color of the hyperlink column doesn't change to white when the row is selected.<br>\r\n<p>Any help is appreciated.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks!<br>\r\n-Larry</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n",
